Track: Student Write Boundary Hardening

Summary:
- Added shared request-level student guard helpers in lib/auth/server.ts.
- Hardened phase completion, assessment submission, spreadsheet draft, and spreadsheet submission routes to reject teacher/admin sessions with 403 before learner-data mutations run.
- Extended route and auth-boundary tests, updated README/security docs, and archived the completed Conductor track.

